---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="VTC Grenoble - Gresse-en-Vercors | Private Shuttle Vercors"
    description="Book your VTC for a transfer between Grenoble and Gresse-en-Vercors. Private driver to take you safely to the foot of the Grand Veymont. Ideal for your hiking or skiing outings.">

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><strong>VTC Grenoble ‚Üî Gresse-en-Vercors</strong></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your private shuttle to easily access the highest village in the Vercors, in summer and winter.</p>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC for Gresse-en-Vercors</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container text-container">
            <h2>Access Nature with Complete Peace of Mind</h2>
            <p>
                Gresse-en-Vercors, nestled at the foot of the Grand Veymont, is a paradise for nature lovers. To get there without worrying about the mountain road, our <strong>VTC driver</strong> service is the ideal solution. We ensure a <strong>safe and comfortable</strong> journey from Grenoble, allowing you to start your hiking or ski day fully refreshed.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why a <strong>Private VTC</strong> for Gresse-en-Vercors?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üèîÔ∏è</div>
                    <h3><strong>Safe Driving</strong> in the Mountains</h3>
                    <p>
                        Enjoy the scenery without stress. Your <a href="/en/about"><strong>experienced driver</strong></a> takes you safely on the Vercors roads, with a <a href="/en/vehicle"><strong>suitable vehicle</strong></a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üéí</div>
                    <h3>Perfect for <strong>Hikers and Skiers</strong></h3>
                    <p>
                        Our vehicle can accommodate your hiking gear, backpacks, or ski equipment. A <strong>door-to-door</strong> service from the center of Grenoble to the trailheads.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">‚úÖ</div>
                    <h3><strong>Flexibility</strong> for your Outings</h3>
                    <p>
                        Whether for a full day, a weekend, or a late return after a hike, we adapt to your schedule for maximum flexibility.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready for a Getaway in the Vercors?</h2>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC Grenoble ‚Üî Gresse-en-Vercors</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root { 
        --accent: #35c2b5; 
        --dark-bg: #2d3a4c;
        --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        --text-color: #333;
    }
    .page-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599827551004-9359f53856d1?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        color: white;
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2em, 5vw, 3.5em); text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7); color: white; }
    .page-hero .subtitle { font-size: 1.2em; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; }
    
    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background-color: var(--accent); 
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px; 
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .content-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .text-container { max-width: 800px; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; }
    .text-container h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .text-container p { font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; }

    .features-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .features-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card .icon { font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .feature-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .feature-card a { font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent); }

    .cta-section {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section h2 { color: white; }
    /* ERREUR CORRIG√âE : Le mot "section" a √©t√© supprim√© */
    .cta-section p { max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; opacity: 0.9; }

    .bg-light { background-color: var(--light-bg); }
    .bg-light .text-container p, .bg-light .feature-card p { color: #333; }
</style>